snippet.textDisplay: Jimmy, your the only late night show I watch. And it’s so disappointing your audience still wears masks, your COVID jokes are not funny unless you can stand some sort of ground. If you think COVID is a joke like it actually is, let your audience free. I’m so disappointed I lost my desire to acquire tickets to your show because of the mask mandate. Get over it dude. Practice what we know you actually think about it. Or maybe I’m wrong. But that shit has to end.
